name: Umana Yana
description: Umana Yana specialises in Guyanese foods which are freshly prepared and cooked on site on a daily basis by the owner. These dishes consist of Guyanese traditional dishes e.g. Pepperpot, Cook-up rice, Metagee, Roti, Curry and many others.
